description: Fetch attributes of an import job.

parameters.description: The identifier of the import job that needs to be retrieved.

nested_items.name: AddressListId
nested_items.description: The unique identifier of the address list the import job was created for.

nested_items.name: CompletedTimestamp
nested_items.description: The timestamp of when the import job was completed.

nested_items.name: CreatedTimestamp
nested_items.description: The timestamp of when the import job was created.

nested_items.name: Error
nested_items.description: The reason for failure of an import job.

nested_items.name: FailedItemsCount
nested_items.description: The number of input addresses that failed to be imported into the address list.

nested_items.name: ImportDataFormat
nested_items.description: The format of the input for an import job.

nested_items.name: ImportDataType
nested_items.description: The type of file that would be passed as an input for the address list import job.

nested_items.name: ImportedItemsCount
nested_items.description: The number of input addresses successfully imported into the address list.

nested_items.name: JobId
nested_items.description: The identifier of the import job.

nested_items.name: Name
nested_items.description: A user-friendly name for the import job.

nested_items.name: PreSignedUrl
nested_items.description: The pre-signed URL target for uploading the input file.

nested_items.name: StartTimestamp
nested_items.description: The timestamp of when the import job was started.

nested_items.name: Status
nested_items.description: The status of the import job.
